                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320906-462-off2606 t18320906-462-crimeloc2608"></join> - then they run off; I went to<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183209060178"></xptr>the gentleman, and asked if he had lost any thing; we followed the prisoners, and in Cross-street I saw them looking at the handkerchief, under a lamp: Krelle put it on his neck - he ran off; he took it off his neck as he run, and threw it down - I took it up, and took him; Cadby brought back Herswell.</p>
